      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend chapter 44 of title 18, United States Code, to enhance penalties for certain thefts of a firearm from certain Federal firearms licensees, and to criminalize the theft of a firearm from a gun range that rents firearms or a shooting club.</title>
      </item>
